<h1>Current Item</h1>
The Current Item area of the workflow tools provides details about the item you are currently working on including information about the item type (ex specimen, region, text etc) as well as the ability to view and update the current status of the item. The status dropdown menu lets you set the status to indicate that you have started work on the item, completed work etc.

